These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different games are played: billiard, domino
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: scientific, time-travel
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, techno
1. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the fan of techno##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Game       | domino       | billiard |
| Beverage         | fanta | hot-chocolate  |
| Movie-Genre       | time-travel    | scientific    |
| Music-Genre   | techno       | gospel      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, disco
There are 2 different favourite colors: chestnut, turquise
House: palace, colonial
2 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard
1. the palace house is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left##1
3. the palace house is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Music-Genre      | disco     | house |
| Color           | chestnut | turquise      |
| House   | colonial  | palace      |
| Pet         | ferret | lizard     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different pets are kept: pony, lizard
2 different games are played: monopoly, poker
City: marseilles, hamburg
House: colonial, victorian
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the pony is the victorian house##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Pet      | pony | lizard  |
| Game          | monopoly    | poker   |
| City   | hamburg  | marseilles   |
| House     | victorian     | colonial |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
City: liverpool, marseilles
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, chaman
2 different games are played: whist, canasta
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
2. the person playing whist is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| City      | liverpool       | marseilles |
| Cigar          | chaman         | ritmeester    |
| Game           | canasta | whist    |
| Sport   | biathlon           | skateboarding   |

