1. the french is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the person eating radish is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Food         | lime | radish   |
| Nationality   | french | indian       |
| Birthday         | december   | june |
| Pet     | horse    | frog     |

