2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person playing go is on the left of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2     |
| Birthday   | february         | august    |
| Sport       | parkour     | ice-hockey  |
| Flower      | daisy | tulip     |
| Game        | go     | backgammon |

