.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, blue
2 different games are played: go, domino
City: boston, hamburg
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, house
1. the person who likes red is on the right of the person playing go##1
2. the person who likes red is on the right of the fan of house##1
3. the person traveling to boston is the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Color           | blue | red     |
| Game   | go          | domino |
| City           | boston          | hamburg    |
| Music-Genre     | house            | r&b       |

 